      "writtenOn": "2026-07-22T17:31:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This is not a user-facing knob. The advertised action-support mask is duplicated across three independently-built components (this translator, the filter-table provider, and the SEL matcher) that cannot share a header; the -DPEF_ACTION_SUPPORT guard lets an integrator raise all of them in lockstep in the same series that wires the additional action, and it defaults to OEM-only when unset. If you would prefer it not be a preprocessor value at all, I can expose it as a meson option instead.",
      "parentUuid": "8d3af7dc_8545c176",
      "revId": "324d9228e08f45c5af3fdfbb66ff4c3af08fe925",
